<p>Traditional share of voice measured how often your brand appeared in organic search results. AI share of voice measures something different: how often AI models mention, recommend, or cite your brand when users ask questions in your category.</p>
<p>We have published 3,500+ blog posts across 70+ industries. This guide covers everything we know about measuring and improving AI share of voice. From manual audits to automated tracking tools to the strategies that actually move the needle.</p>
